{"tid":971594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"揾人屌醒，thx","createTime":"2019-01-06T18:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T09:03:22.000Z","uid":221993,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f178b63d8bee493f26d2d294fce71bc5b422a6","tid":971594,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"當初好賤咁飛人，後尾又後悔。真係有原因，個原因仲要好on9。都一段時間冇揾佢，平安夜揾返。有傾下計，幾好，朋友。<br />\n但有日佢叫我唔好再揾佢，話佢真係接受唔到。仲block咗我wts。我先知真係冇可能，冇可能再一齊，連朋友都冇可能再做。即使係咁，我都係放唔底&hellip;<br />\n想揾人屌醒我。日日訓之前又係諗起佢，去邊只要係同佢去過都會諗起。望住件著過嚟同佢出街嘅衫又會諗起。好痛苦。<br />\n我認我賤，但係咪真係得時間先沖淡到？<br />\n對唔住吖&hellip;我咁對你，真係好錯。<br />\n我係賤到，你有啲野係知嘅，你都唔出聲，仲一直咁包容同比愛我。同你一齊嘅日子真係好幸福，好甜&hellip;<br />\n對唔住&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"55e79e3dfc1964a0d77eb46539e39435f116c222","tid":971594,"uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T18:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FULX9ym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFULX9ym.png&h=f1e12be5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dafabac26b75dc1a00b855b4fb0b240ed6ebe1b9","tid":971594,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e79e3dfc1964a0d77eb46539e39435f116c222","tid":971594,"uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T18:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FULX9ym.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFULX9ym.png&h=f1e12be5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"再屌，未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d290886cdcef42e55e53d1384905c442cf2f61","tid":971594,"uid":23815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦臭雞<br />\n咁有原因大大聲講埋出黎大家幫你圍爐取暖呀嘛<br />\n講啲唔講啲"},{"pid":"c0eedd6113a89916f05b66a684b881b6b9ecc1d6","tid":971594,"uid":221993,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b4d290886cdcef42e55e53d1384905c442cf2f61","tid"